        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>kVAR</strong></td>
          <td>Kilovolt-Ampere Reactive</td>
          <td>Reactive power — the "foam" in the mug</td>
          <td><code>kVAR = √(kVA² − kW²)</code></td>
          <td>Power factor correction capacitor sizing</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>W</strong></td>
          <td>Watt</td>
          <td>Real power (same as kW, smaller unit)</td>
